  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of water to a boil and cook the noodles according to package instructions.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the Thai green curry paste to the skillet and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the shrimp to the skillet and cook until pink, about 2-3 minutes per side.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice, orange zest, salt, and pepper.",
    "Combine the cooked noodles and shrimp mixture in a large bowl.",
    "Sprinkle the grated tempering chocolate over the top of the noodles.",
    "Serve the noodles on a talavera plate and garnish with additional orange zest if desired."
